engine-title: Reasonable defaults
engine-doc: |+
  This is not intended to be hard preference
  for Pen.el that always delegates engines to
  prompts. Rather, it's a good go-to that a
  prompt may specify, along with a set of
  requirements.
vendor: various vendors
# Select the first which satisfies the requirements
family:
- OpenAI Curie
- OpenAI Instruct
- OpenAI Davinci
- OpenAI Codex
# Unless, for specific requirements, defer
defer:
- nl+code: OpenAI Codex
- code: OpenAI Codex
- nl: OpenAI Davinci
- nl-task: OpenAI Instruct
- speed: OpenAI Curie
fallback: OpenAI